comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_RWA_REPORT_FB_INVEST_TMP.product_type
  is '分类标记： CF01 普通票据 CF02 供应链票据 CF03 等分化票据';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_RWA_REPORT_FB_INVEST_TMP.asset_thd_cls_cd
